      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST QUICKLY (2) was a winner (22.28) at Warrnambool two back but out of the placings last time when 6th at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MORAINE PIPER (3) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 3 length third over 425m at this track, clocking 24.40. Leading player again. KRAKEN BABE (6) is progressing well scoring last time out (24.19) at this track and bringing up her 6th career win. Has a good record here including three wins. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of the leading chances again. BENGAL BULLET (1) form at this course and distance reads well.",
